OL,3,CExcavation to identify 796 babies and
OL,4,Cchildren buried in septic tank
OL,6,FThe first mass forensic exhumation has
OL,7,Fbegun at the site of a former Irish
OL,8,FCatholic mother and baby institution,
OL,9,Fwhere it's believed the bodies of
OL,10,Falmost 800 babies and children are
OL,11,Fburied in a disused sewage tank.
OL,13,FThe former site of St Mary's Mother
OL,14,Fand Baby Home, in the town of Tuam,
OL,15,FCounty Galway, was boarded up on
OL,16,FMonday as forensic teams began the
OL,17,Fexcavation process, expected to take
OL,18,Faround two years.
