OL,6,FThe former institution, which operated
OL,7,Fbetween 1925 and 1961, was run by the
OL,8,FBon Secours Sisters, a religious order
OL,9,Fof Catholic nuns, as a maternity home
OL,10,Ffor unmarried mothers and their
OL,11,Fchildren.
OL,13,FThe building was demolished after it
OL,14,Fclosed and the site, including a
OL,15,Fmemorial garden for the dead, is now
OL,16,Fsituated in the middle of a housing
OL,17,Festate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
