OL,6,FAnnette McKay, who lives in Greater
OL,7,FManchester, believes her sister Mary
OL,8,FMargaret O'Connor is one of the babies
OL,9,Fburied on the Co Galway site.
OL,11,FMary died at the institution aged six-
OL,12,Fweeks old in 1943 from whooping cough
OL,13,Fand heart failure. Her mother, Maggie
OL,14,FO'Connor, was told "your child of sin
OL,15,Fis dead" and denied a funeral or
OL,16,Fproper burial for her baby.
OL,18,F"Today feels overwhelming, after a
OL,19,Fdecade of campaigning, delays and
OL,20,Fobfuscation the exhumation will
OL,21,Fbegin," Ms McKay told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
