OL,6,F"I hope every child is identified and
OL,7,Fburied with dignity and respect. As a
OL,8,Fmember of the advisory board I know
OL,9,Fhow difficult and complex this whole
OL,10,Fprocess will be. My thoughts and
OL,11,Fprayers are with all the survivors and
OL,12,Ffamilies."
OL,14,FMs O'Connor died in 2016 after
OL,15,Fsuffering years of torment over the
OL,16,Funanswered questions around the death
OL,17,Fof her firstborn.
