OL,6,FThe Office of the Director of
OL,7,FAuthorised Interventions at Tuam
OL,8,F(ODAIT), led by Daniel MacSweeney, a
OL,9,Fformer International Committee of the
OL,10,FRed Cross envoy, is in charge of
OL,11,Fexhuming the bodies.
OL,13,FODAIT say the purpose of the work is
OL,14,Fto "restore dignity in death and,
OL,15,Fwhere possible, an identity to those
OL,16,Finappropriately buried at the site".
OL,18,FIt is hoped this will give relatives
OL,19,Fand survivors the chance to hold a
OL,20,Fdignified reburial for their loved
OL,21,Fones.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
