OL,6,FHowever, the process will be
OL,7,F"challenging" due to the young age of
OL,8,Fthe children, the elapse of time since
OL,9,Ftheir death, the environmental
OL,10,Fconditions in Tuam, and the "likely
OL,11,Fsmall number of close relatives who
OL,12,Fcan provide samples", ODAIT says.
OL,14,FOnce the initial set-up stages are
OL,15,Fcomplete, the team will begin digging
OL,16,Fthe ground in mid July, starting at
OL,17,Fthe playground and finishing at the
OL,18,Farea known as the children's mass
OL,19,Fgrave.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
