OL,6,FLast week it was reported that a
OL,7,Fpolice investigation could be launched
OL,8,Fif the forensic specialists uncover
OL,9,Fevidence that any of the infants died
OL,10,Funlawfully.
OL,12,FSpeaking to the Irish Examiner, a
OL,13,Fspokesperson for ODAIT said if any of
OL,14,Fthe children died unnaturally, or if
OL,15,Fany remains found do not belong to
OL,16,Fchildren who lived at the home, gardai
OL,17,Fwill be notified.
