OL,6,FEarlier this year, ITV News revealed
OL,7,Fthat as many as 10,000 women and
OL,8,Fbabies may have been deported from
OL,9,FBritain to Ireland between 1931 and
OL,10,F1977.
OL,12,FThose children, now adults, often only
OL,13,Ffound out they were British citizens
OL,14,Fdecades later.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
