OL,6,FDr Lorraine Grimes from Maynooth
OL,7,FUniversity has spent a decade
OL,8,Finvestigating these institutions. Her
OL,9,Fresearch interviews with survivors
OL,10,Ffound that many were forced to travel,
OL,11,Fsome while heavily pregnant, against
OL,12,Ftheir will.
OL,14,FThose mothers and their young children
OL,15,Fwould have been transferred to similar
OL,16,Finstitutions like the Mother and Baby
OL,17,FHome in Tuam.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
