OL,6,F"They were prison-like institutions
OL,7,Ffocused on rehabilitation of the
OL,8,Fwoman's 'sin' - the sin being to have
OL,9,Fa child outside of marriage," Dr
OL,10,FGrimes told ITV News.
OL,12,F"These institutions were places of
OL,13,Fpunishment and those who had more than
OL,14,Fone child outside of marriage were
OL,15,Ftreated more harshly."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
