OL,6,F'My baby was kidnapped': ITV News
OL,7,Ftravels to Dublin to speak to victims
OL,8,Fof a 'horror' forced repatriation
OL,9,Fscheme run by British and Irish
OL,10,FCatholic and state organisations for
OL,11,Fdecades
OL,13,FIn 2021 the Irish Taoiseach Micheal
OL,14,FMartin delivered a formal apology for
OL,15,Fhistoric forced adoption and the
OL,16,Fsuffering caused.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
