OL,6,FSpeaking about the excavation on
OL,7,FMonday, Mr Martin said: "It's very
OL,8,Fsignificant day in respect of the
OL,9,Fexcavation in Tuam.
OL,11,F"It's a very, very difficult harrowing
OL,12,Fstory and situation. We have to wait
OL,13,Fto see what unfolds now as a result of
OL,14,Fthe excavation."
OL,16,FPatrick Rodgers, regional manager of
OL,17,Fthe charity Frea, runs the group
OL,18,F'Renewing Roots' which supports those
OL,19,Fwho were born or gave birth in
OL,20,FIreland's institutions and now live in
OL,21,Fthe North of England.
