OL,6,F"The beginning of exhumation work at
OL,7,Fthe grounds of the Tuam Mother and
OL,8,FBaby institution is a vital step to
OL,9,Frestoring some measure of dignity to
OL,10,Fthose whose deaths and manner of
OL,11,Fburial caused so much anguish," he
OL,12,Ftold ITV News.
OL,14,F"At this time we remember the loved
OL,15,Fones of those buried at the site as
OL,16,Fwell as those who are buried at other
OL,17,Finstitutions across the country."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
